snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 - Enemies: Tyranid Swarms
snippet.description:
Confront relentless hordes of Tyranids in Space Marine 2.

Harnessing their hive mind, they strike as one. Arm yourself and charge into the fray.

#SpaceMarine2 launches on September 9. Pre-orders are now open.
